{"tid":33892,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"新手買機一問","createTime":"2016-12-11T06:32:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-11T09:07:15.000Z","uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"203b0731ec839e77b84d531256a182928df4fd74","tid":33892,"uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:32:09.000Z","msg":"就黎放個半月SEM BREAK，<br />\n<br />\n中學接觸過攝影，有興趣，但無經濟能力買。<br />\n<br />\n宜家終於有機會，1516緊買邊部，<br />\n<br />\n有幾部心水既(綜合網上推薦)，如下:<br />\n<br />\n1. Olympus Pen E-PL 7/8<br />\n2. Fujifilm X-A2 / X-A3<br />\n3. Panasonic Lumix DMC-LX100<br />\n<br />\nC牌同N牌唔識揀，求各位巴絲幫手揀下邊部好D同值得買<br />\n<br />\n我無乜要求，見哩幾部重量差唔多，中意影景多過人像，<br />\n<br />\n想問下邊度影天空/星星好D，想要D夜晚影相都唔太差既。<br />\n<br />\n唔一定要哩幾部，可以係其他推薦，筆直係5000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e8f92e198358a0f98f30142d9972f089d73bcb3","tid":33892,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:38:54.000Z","msg":"要影星既話 呢3部 我會揀富士"},{"pid":"893a10431352a271d784b7e2084013701d2e2034","tid":33892,"uid":28428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:41:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要影星既話 呢3部 我會揀富士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇，好多都推薦X-A2，<br />\n但我見佢出左X-A3，<br />\n其實想知新同舊版有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0994380ded2c6e9f17352585023a89f724e27224","tid":33892,"uid":30794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-11T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要影星既話 呢3部 我會揀富士</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇，好多都推薦X-A2，<br />\n但我見佢出左X-A3，<br />\n其實想知新同舊版有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔熟富士 答你唔到"},{"pid":"09497e0a